    <p style="text-align:center"><a href="https://www.marbleheadschools.org/district/files/remote-learning-plan" target="_blank"><strong>MPS Remote Learning Plan</strong></a></p>
<p>The Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) is an evolving situation that we are monitoring closely. The North Shore area superintendents have collaborated to make a timely and unified decision about school closure in the best interests of faculty, staff, students, and families.This decision was made after significant conversations among school leaders, local public health officials, and state officials. Our Administrative Team has met for a number of hours over several days to detail a plan to provide a continuity of education experiences. We strongly urge our families to familiarize themselves with the Social Distancing recommendations and the additional information listed below. </p>
